## ğŸ“¦ Installation

**From PyPI**
```bash
pip install llm-evaluation-framework
```

**From Source**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/isathish/LLMEvaluationFramework.git
cd LLMEvaluationFramework
pip install -e .[dev]
```

